      HOW TO UPDATE FOR EACH RELEASE
      ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      1. Duplicate the <item> block below and make it the first item.
      2. Update: title, sparkle:version (CFBundleVersion integer),
         sparkle:shortVersionString, pubDate, description.
      3. Set enclosure url= to the .pkg URL under /downloads/apple/.
      4. Set enclosure length= (byte count):
             stat -f%z releases/InterlinedList-X.Y.Z-label.pkg
      5. Set sparkle:edSignature= (run after building the .pkg):
             <sparkle>/bin/sign_update releases/InterlinedList-X.Y.Z-label.pkg <private-key>
